http://lkml.org/lkml/2006/3/31/82,
 even with 2.6.17-rc6.
> >>
> >>Trond Myklebust have created a patch which we have verified solves this
> >>problem for 2.6.16, 2.6.17-rc4 and 2.6.17-rc6. The patch is available
